graph TB
    subgraph "RHODS Operator"
        ControllerMgr[Controller Manager<br/>Main Process]
        DSCInitCtrl[DSCInitialization Controller<br/>Platform Initialization]
        DSCCtrl[DataScienceCluster Controller<br/>Component Lifecycle]
        SecretGen[SecretGenerator Controller<br/>Credential Management]
        CertGen[CertConfigmapGenerator Controller<br/>Certificate Distribution]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>Admission Control]
        Metrics[Metrics Exporter<br/>Prometheus]

        ControllerMgr --> DSCInitCtrl
        ControllerMgr --> DSCCtrl
        ControllerMgr --> SecretGen
        ControllerMgr --> CertGen
        ControllerMgr --> Webhook
        ControllerMgr --> Metrics
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        DSC[DataScienceCluster CR<br/>datasciencecluster.opendatahub.io/v1]
        DSCI[DSCInitialization CR<br/>dscinitialization.opendatahub.io/v1]
        FT[FeatureTracker CR<br/>features.opendatahub.io/v1]
    end

    subgraph "Managed Components"
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
        Workbenches[Workbenches/Notebooks]
        KServe[KServe]
        ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving]
        Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines]
        CodeFlare[CodeFlare]
        Ray[KubeRay]
        Kueue[Kueue]
        TrustyAI[TrustyAI]
    end

    subgraph "Platform Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
        Istio[Istio Service Mesh]
        Prometheus[Prometheus Operator]
        CertManager[cert-manager]
        OAuth[OpenShift OAuth]
    end

    User[Administrator] -->|creates| DSC
    User -->|creates| DSCI

    DSC -->|watched by| DSCCtrl
    DSCI -->|watched by| DSCInitCtrl
    FT -->|managed by| DSCCtrl

    Webhook -->|validates/mutates| DSC
    Webhook -->|validates/mutates| DSCI

    DSCCtrl -->|deploys| Dashboard
    DSCCtrl -->|deploys| Workbenches
    DSCCtrl -->|deploys| KServe
    DSCCtrl -->|deploys| ModelMesh
    DSCCtrl -->|deploys| Pipelines
    DSCCtrl -->|deploys| CodeFlare
    DSCCtrl -->|deploys| Ray
    DSCCtrl -->|deploys| Kueue
    DSCCtrl -->|deploys| TrustyAI

    DSCInitCtrl -->|configures| Istio
    DSCInitCtrl -->|configures| Prometheus
    DSCInitCtrl -->|creates namespaces| K8sAPI

    SecretGen -->|generates| K8sAPI
    CertGen -->|generates| K8sAPI

    ControllerMgr -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    DSCCtrl -->|uses| CertManager
    DSCCtrl -->|integrates| OAuth

    Metrics -->|exposes to| Prometheus

    style ControllerMgr fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
